ISLAMABAD, Jun 11 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Saturday congratulated Muhammad Asif for winning the WBA South Super Flyweight boxing title.
In a statement, he said the youth of Pakistan had a lot of talent in the field of sports.Youth could further shine the name of the country with encouragement and better training, he added.
